CPAN-Mini-FromList

Generate a CPAN Mirror consisting of a defined list of modules.

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

    perl Build.PL
    ./Build
    ./Build test
    ./Build install


SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the perldoc command.

    perldoc CPAN::Mini::FromList

You can also look for information at:

    Search CPAN
        http://search.cpan.org/dist/CPAN-Mini-FromList

    CPAN Request Tracker:
        http://rt.cpan.org/NoAuth/Bugs.html?Dist=CPAN-Mini-FromList

    AnnoCPAN, annotated CPAN documentation:
        http://annocpan.org/dist/CPAN-Mini-FromList

    CPAN Ratings:
        http://cpanratings.perl.org/d/CPAN-Mini-FromList

